---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<p>
				Hey there! 👋 <br /><br />I'm a sixteen-year-old web developer
				with a passion for design and a love for food <span>🍔🍰</span>.
				In this digital diary, I'm going to share my thoughts,
				experiences, and everything in between. Whether it's a new
				coding adventure, a delicious culinary discovery, or just some
				random musings, you're invited to join me on this exciting
				journey.
			</p><br />
			<p>
				If you're into web design, you're in the right place! I'll be
				dishing out tips, tricks, and creative inspiration to help you
				level up your design game. From UI/UX insights to the latest
				trends in web development, we've got it all covered.
			</p><br />
			<p>
				But that's not all! This blog is also a space for me to express
				myself, share my thoughts on life, and connect with fellow
				enthusiasts. Think of it as a mix of code, cuisine, and candid
				conversations.
			</p><br />
			<p>
				So, grab a virtual seat at my digital table, and let's embark on
				this adventure together. <span>🚀</span> Get ready to code,
				cook, and connect! <span>🍽️💬</span>
			</p><br />
			<p>
				Thanks for dropping by, and I can't wait to share this
				incredible journey with you. Stay tuned for more! <span
					>📆📚🌐</span
				>
			</p><br />
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
